1.01.name: wordpress/restaurant
1.01.description: Restaurant Theme is a easy to use but functional responsive theme for restaurant website that works on any device. Features include a front page template with it's own loading page, an intergrated slider library to manage sliders. With optional Google Map Shortcode plugins and SimpleBooings Online Booking Form plugins (not included, available at Designpromote.co.uk/wordpress), you can build a fully functioned restaurant website. Though, it may work with other types of business. The theme is a child theme of Twenty Twelve.
